---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<section class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-cinzel text-darkest-blue mb-4">Ceník pro rok {currentYear}</h2>
    <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-dark-blue mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="price-card group">
      <div
        class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-background-blue p-6 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute -right-12 -top-12 h-24 w-24 rotate-12 transform bg-light-blue opacity-20 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:rotate-45"
        >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-cinzel text-darkest-blue mb-4">Individuální konzultace</h3>
        <div class="price-tag">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark-blue">1000 Kč</span>
          <span class="text-darkest-blue opacity-70">/ 50 minut</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="price-card group">
      <div
        class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-background-blue p-6 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute -right-12 -top-12 h-24 w-24 rotate-12 transform bg-light-blue opacity-20 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:rotate-45"
        >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-cinzel text-darkest-blue mb-4">Skupinová konzultace</h3>
        <div class="price-tag">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark-blue">1200 Kč</span>
          <span class="text-darkest-blue opacity-70">/ 50 minut</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="price-card group md:col-span-2">
      <div
        class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-background-blue p-6 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute -right-12 -top-12 h-24 w-24 rotate-12 transform bg-light-blue opacity-20 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:rotate-45"
        >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-cinzel text-darkest-blue mb-4">
          Konzultace s reflektujícím týmem
        </h3>
        <p class="text-darkest-blue opacity-80">
          Po dohodě s Vámi mohu na konzultaci přizvat další odborníky a odbornice, kteří po jeho
          skončení sdělí své postřehy. Mohou Vám tak nabídnout alternativní možnosti.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .price-card {
    perspective: 1000px;
  }

  .price-card > div {
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .price-card:hover > div {
    transform: translateY(-5px) rotateX(2deg);
  }

  .price-tag {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0% {
      transform: translateY(0px);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateY(0px);
    }
  }

  .price-card:hover .absolute {
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>
